### 1. GET all vehicles
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Vehicles

### 2. GET available vehicles
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Vehicles?$filter=status eq 'Available'

### 3. GET shipments with status InTransit
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments?$filter=status eq 'InTransit'

### 4. GET all shipments for a specific customer
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments?$filter=customerId eq 'C01'

### 5. GET routes between two cities
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Routes?$filter=fromCity eq 'Mumbai' and toCity eq 'Pune'

### 6. GET drivers sorted by rating descending
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Drivers?$orderby=rating desc

### 7. GET all active routes
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Routes?$filter=isActive eq true

### 8. POST a new shipment booking
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ID": "SH09",
  "trackingNumber": "SL-2026-00009",
  "customerId": "C01",
  "driverId": "D01",
  "vehicleId": "V01",
  "pickupAddress": "123 MG Road",
  "deliveryAddress": "456 FC Road",
  "pickupCity": "Mumbai",
  "deliveryCity": "Pune",
  "weight": 300,
  "status": "Booked",
  "bookedAt": "2024-06-01T10:00:00",
  "estimatedDelivery": "2024-06-03",
  "charges": 2500,
  "paymentStatus": "Pending"
}

### 9. PATCH shipment status to Delivered
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments(ID='SH02')
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Delivered",
  "deliveredAt": "2024-05-08T14:00:00"
}

### 10. GET drivers that are available
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Drivers?$filter=status eq 'Available'

### 11. GET shipments sorted by charges descending
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments?$orderby=charges desc

### 12. GET top 3 shipments
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments?$top=3

### 13. GET vehicles with select fields
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/logistics/Vehicles?$select=ID,registrationNumber,type,status